_sText:
This map took me forever because I'm lazy and a bad mapper, I eventually got there though.

Map is made for legit and auto, possible on both difficulties. I haven't done much play testing on how fast the map can be done. It is all BHOP, there is no Longjump's or Climbs involved.

I am not creative with names so I just called it bhop_dream2, already made a bhop_dream >:3

Thanks to all that helped, have fun :D
